{"level":"INFO","time":"2026-04-15T16:02:10.073+0800","caller":"service/generate_service.go:39","msg":"提取文本成功Speaker Johnson, can I ask you about the president's post defecting himself as Jesus? Was it blasphemy? >> I talked with the president about it as soon as I saw it and um told him that I don't think it was uh being received in the same way he intended it. He agreed and he pulled it down. That was the right thing to do. He explained how he saw that and um I don't think he thought it was sacrilegious at all. So, >> do you think he should back down? >> I think he showed great great respect to others by removing it. Speaker Johnson, can I ask you about the president's post supporting himself as Jesus? Was it blasphemy? >> I talked with the president about it as soon as I saw it and um told him that I don't think it was uh being received in the same way he intended it. He agreed and he pulled it down. That was the right thing to do. He explained how he saw that and um I don't think he thought it was sacrilegious at all. So, >> do you think he should back? >> I think he showed great great respect to others by removing it."}
